---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { siteConfig } from '../config';
---

<BaseLayout title="关于" description={siteConfig.description}>
  <section class="about-hero" data-reveal>
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
      <p class="hero-persona">你好，我是杨雨飞。</p>
      <h1>{siteConfig.name}</h1>
      <p class="lead">{siteConfig.description}</p>
    </div>
    <img class="about-avatar" src="https://github.com/duolaBmeng673.png" alt="杨雨飞的 GitHub 头像" />
  </section>

  <section class="about-grid" aria-label="个人详情">
    <article class="detail-panel" data-reveal data-tilt>
      <p class="panel-label">Education</p>
      <h2>{siteConfig.education}</h2>
      <p>信息安全专业背景，持续关注软件系统、算法能力和 AI 应用之间的连接。</p>
    </article>

    <article class="detail-panel" data-reveal data-tilt>
      <p class="panel-label">Focus</p>
      <div class="tag-list">
        {siteConfig.tags.map((tag) => <span>{tag}</span>)}
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="detail-panel wide" data-reveal data-tilt>
      <p class="panel-label">Now</p>
      <h2>记录学习、工程和长期思考</h2>
      <p>
        这个博客会作为一个持续更新的知识空间：把项目里的判断、读到的概念、踩过的坑和重新想明白的问题沉淀下来。
      </p>
      <a class="text-link" href={siteConfig.github} target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">访问 GitHub</a>
    </article>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
